{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b7b19e2dc7","title":"常风等人的右派言论","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（四）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编印，1957年11月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b4ef69fdc6","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"b7b19e2dc7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"79af059482","name":"山西师范学院"},{"id":"8fb6588f9f","name":"田雨翔"},{"id":"de56f35222","name":"班书阁"},{"id":"f80fe6bf67","name":"常风"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4eed4ff9cb","type":"title","text":"常风等人的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7b19e2dc7"},{"id":"b123e807b9","type":"authors","text":"山西师范学院常风田雨翔班书阁","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7b19e2dc7"},{"id":"1dbb925d90","type":"paragraph","text":"常风（山西师范学院教授）：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7b19e2dc7"},{"id":"82664b1237","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）“苏联把某些科学发明的创造记在自己的账上了，如蒸汽机的发明……”。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7b19e2dc7"},{"id":"9373bac1eb","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）学校外语系曾聘请一位苏联专家的爱人，给俄语组同学讲课，有时招待些糖、茶，他认为这是“特殊待遇”又说：“‘北大’时有一位美国教授跟中国教授的待遇一样，我坚持不聘10年制教员，拉洋车的能说外国话，但教不了书（苏联10年制毕业也教不了大学）”。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7b19e2dc7"},{"id":"9472c77463","type":"paragraph","text":"田雨翔（山西师范学院教授、民盟省筹委组织部长）：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7b19e2dc7"},{"id":"4db8800d38","type":"paragraph","text":"“共产党是一个封建王朝、互相撕杀的宗派集团；如果贝利亚不死，马林科夫也垮不了台”。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7b19e2dc7"},{"id":"097301de32","type":"paragraph","text":"班书阁（山西师范学院教授、民盟支部委员）：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7b19e2dc7"},{"id":"9b4d9834a7","type":"paragraph","text":"“‘德’是会舔领导的屁股；‘才’是舔的领导很舒服；‘资’是舔的次数很多。”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7b19e2dc7"}],"page":{"id":"f10e30fc52","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7b19e2dc7","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}